\v 11  \w I|strong="H5704"\w* replied, “\w How|strong="H4970"\w* \w long|strong="H5704"\w*, sovereign \w master|strong="H3427"\w*?” \w He|strong="H5704"\w* said,  
\q1 “\w Until|strong="H5704"\w* \w cities|strong="H5892"\w* \w are|strong="H5892"\w* \w in|strong="H3427"\w* \w ruins|strong="H5892"\w* \w and|strong="H1004"\w* unpopulated,  
